reviewText: I  like it because, it helps  me  to teach, my Granddaughter her ABC.

I wish I'd realized how OLD this DVD was - probably first recorded on reel to reel.  I teach KR/transitional kindergarten and my students wouldn't watch it.  It moves too slow, the main character is scary-not charming and the sound is not true. Sadly I didn't open the package right away so when I did it was too late to return - otherwise I would have.
